@baseUrl = http://localhost:5140/api/menus/search

### Search all menus (from Elasticsearch)
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Search menus by text
GET {{baseUrl}}?q=lunch

### Search menus by item type
GET {{baseUrl}}?itemType=restaurant

### Search menus by owner
GET {{baseUrl}}?ownerId=rest-001

### Search active menus only
GET {{baseUrl}}?active=true

### Search with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}?page=1&size=10

### Get menu by ID from ES
# Replace {menuId} with a real menu ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/{menuId}
